summary: Aegisters are a elven race that have lived deep in the caves of Morrowind for thousands of year, and have spent their time learning to master the arcane arts, unfortunately, due to their dabbling in the black books of Hermaeus Mora, they have been curse to roam Tamriel as wooden monsters.
